{"tid":978744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「跟女優啪不是夢！」AV達人曝：女優見面會上色釣男影迷","createTime":"2019-01-12T06:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T07:09:05.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ff375645b0967a1e99ddffee30f60480098ea9c2","tid":978744,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"日本AV女優在男性的心中都有著「特別的地位」，然而若是能和女優們面對面互動，對於男性或粉絲來說就已經是無比欣慰，然而卻有女優超級大膽，AV達人「一劍浣春秋」就爆料，有女優承認會勾引「參加見面會的影迷成為炮友」。<br />\n <br />\n熟知日本情色產業的，AV達人「一劍浣春秋」日前又揭露，經紀公司LINX旗下的女優「愛里留衣（愛里るい）」私底下就是一個相當縱慾的女生，而愛里留衣曾在電視節目中坦承，自己的炮友就多達700人，而且她至今仍繼續在找「床伴」。<br />\n <br />\n一劍浣春秋也透露，愛里留衣就連在見面會上看對眼的影迷，都會準備「私藏小禮物」裡面就有自己的連絡方式，只要對方OK，愛里留衣也會大方的邀約對方上床，然而愛里留衣也曾坦承自己「要的很多」，也會讓許多男生害怕，通常3小時裡會連續要個４.5次，這樣的魔鬼條件，也讓不少網友笑稱「敢接也真的要有真本事啊」。"},{"pid":"1180743e57d50a9149da3f1574d2daea86169c53","tid":978744,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:58:03.000Z","msg":"講還講"},{"pid":"d4a6cb62db3c87f3f30bc4222e5f8dd849162524","tid":978744,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wG97qWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwG97qWa.png&h=fc570286&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6fca199b868903f1ee4f9567b4f522a4baa0f8b","tid":978744,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"4.5次點計出黎"},{"pid":"e73587427bc95862a78b56a1fe1978b76e5089ab","tid":978744,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"廣告宣傳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65958a5a22cc2828d9151b99a4637a9998ba704","tid":978744,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"唔收錢先講啦"},{"pid":"82ee82fa738e35de4d7aea8b9cf802193331d46f","tid":978744,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:04:34.000Z","msg":"唔怪得會有女優瀨左野傳染俾人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a36c09b6b49e4d806bcf0b8dfdb698823ee663","tid":978744,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4a6cb62db3c87f3f30bc4222e5f8dd849162524","tid":978744,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wG97qWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwG97qWa.png&h=fc570286&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"ee8379da13a8fa7490ff5f55a44254472ae6b1d5","tid":978744,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"睇得太多呢類文。<br />\n假到仆街。<br />\n作大D 好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}